fields.Title: INITIATION / SPEED HABIT
fields.Description: A thought for becoming a speed addict.

fields.Title: Composure: "Whooh, this shit is strong. This sh..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Whooh, this shit is strong. This shit is disco.

fields.Title: Electrochemistry: "You raise the bottle, close a nostr..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You raise the bottle, close a nostril and inhale *furiously*. The rush is almost immediate. It tastes bitter and caustic, and stings a bit inside your nose.

fields.Title: You: "Okay, my body is ready. Let's do th..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Okay, my body is ready. Let's do this. (Try some speed.)

fields.Title: Electrochemistry: "See, that's your problem -- a lack..."
fields.Dialogue Text: See, that's your problem -- a lack of confidence. Speed can help you with that. It can help you with EVERYTHING.
fields.Alternate1: See, that's your problem -- a lack of confidence. Speed can help you with that *and* Kim. It can help you with EVERYTHING.

fields.Title: Electrochemistry: "To *this*? You kidding?! There are..."
fields.Dialogue Text: To *this*? You kidding?! There are downsides to *not* being on it.

fields.Title: Tutorial Agent: "In the bottom right corner of the s..."
fields.Dialogue Text: In the bottom right corner of the screen there's a SPEED button! SPEED gives +1 to MOTORIC skills: Perception, Reaction Speed, Hand/Eye Coordination, Savoir Faire, Interfacing, and Composure. This is good before a White Check -- but damages your Morale.

fields.Title: Electrochemistry: "Spring-spring! Everything is clear..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Spring-spring! Everything is clear around you. You're ready to concentrate on the next task in the task chain.

fields.Title: Electrochemistry: "You raise the Preptide bottle, pres..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You raise the Preptide bottle, press one nostril closed, and inhale *furiously* with the other. The rush is almost immediate. It tastes bitter and caustic, and stings a bit inside your nose.

fields.Title: Electrochemistry: "It will make you into *more* than t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It will make you into *more* than that -- a Megacop! This is your modus operandi. This is how you've done it for *years*. Let's go!

fields.Title: Kim Kitsuragi: ""I'm not your mother." He avoids yo..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "I'm not your mother." He avoids your gaze. "I don't care. Do what you have to do."

fields.Title: You: "Mamma mia!"
fields.Dialogue Text: Mamma mia!

fields.Title: But you need the zeal. Let's face it, you're never going to finish this case without some extra help.
You: "This is gonna be really bad for my..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This is gonna be really bad for my health, isn't it?

fields.Title: Electrochemistry: "You raise the bottle, close a nostr..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You raise the bottle, close a nostril and inhale *furiously*. The rush is almost immediate. It tastes bitter and caustic, and stings a bit inside your nose.

fields.Title: Electrochemistry: "You raise the Preptide bottle, pres..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You raise the Preptide bottle, press one nostril closed, and inhale *furiously* with the other. The rush is almost immediate. It tastes bitter and caustic, and stings a bit inside your nose.

fields.Title: Electrochemistry: "This is so unprofessional of you. T..."
fields.Dialogue Text: This is so unprofessional of you. Think you can ignore this -- your *moral compass* telling you to sniff it? Guess again -- you'll be back here soon. You'll get the chance to choose more wisely.

fields.Title: Jump to: [But you need the zeal. Let's face it, you're never going to finish this case without some extra help.]
Electrochemistry: "Now that you've acquired some stimu..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Now that you've acquired some stimulants, it's time for a little pick-me-up. Time to *detect*.

fields.Title: You: "Will it make me into a Supercop?"
fields.Dialogue Text: Will it make me into a Supercop?

fields.Title: You: ""Kim, I did a little speed. I hope..."
fields.Dialogue Text: "Kim, I did a little speed. I hope you don't mind. It was for professional reasons."

fields.Title: Tutorial Agent: "You've passed up your chance to sta..."
fields.Dialogue Text: You've passed up your chance to start using SPEED for now, but don't worry! The option to use it becomes available again in 1 hour.

fields.Title: Electrochemistry: "It's not ideal, no... But you need..."
fields.Dialogue Text: It's not ideal, no... But you need the zeal. Let's face it, you're never going to finish this case without cheating.

fields.Title: You: ""Hngfff...""
fields.Dialogue Text: "Hngfff..."

fields.Title: You: "Feels great. Are there *any* downsi..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Feels great. Are there *any* downsides to this at all?

fields.Title: You: "What... but right *here*? Now?"
fields.Dialogue Text: What... but right *here*? Now?
fields.Alternate1: Wait, but Kim is here. He'll be dissappointed.

fields.Title: Esprit de Corps: "As long as you remain functional, h..."
fields.Dialogue Text: As long as you remain functional, he thinks. Now let's get back to work.

fields.Title: Suggestion: "Time for a little truth. Tell the l..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Time for a little truth. Tell the lieutenant you did some, clear the air.

fields.Title: You: "I'm not doing this now. [Ignore tho..."
fields.Dialogue Text: I'm not doing this now. [Ignore thought.]

fields.Title: Logic: "Hmmm, you could work with this high..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Hmmm, you could work with this high... Like, literally *work*: Solve the case, file some papers. Maybe clean up your hostel room, then solve *another* case, then start a side investigation into the para-natural, then build a radiocomputer...

fields.Title: You: "Cool, cool, let's boogie. [Finish t..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Cool, cool, let's boogie. [Finish thought and spring to action.]

fields.Title: Electrochemistry: "Now the taste is slowly receding in..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Now the taste is slowly receding into your throat... The rush is growing in intensity, your little heart pounding like a bird in a cage. A sweat breaks out across your brow, your jaw clenches...

fields.Title: Endurance: "And, let's be honest, there's a lit..."
fields.Dialogue Text: And, let's be honest, there's a little chest pain -- the *good* kind, of course. You may wanna blast a Nosaphed or something.

fields.Title: Volition: "There are *massive* downsides. It's..."
fields.Dialogue Text: There are *massive* downsides. It's a potent neurotoxin. You're turning yourself into a frayed idiot.

fields.Title: Jump to: [But you need the zeal. Let's face it, you're never going to finish this case without some extra help.]
You: "Good to have you back, Officer Supe..."
fields.Dialogue Text: Good to have you back, Officer Supercop. The world has been waiting.
fields.Alternate1: Good to have you back, Officer Megacop. The world has been waiting.
